metadata.name: Squid Game Mask's Gold
metadata.description:
For my very first entry on Foundation, I decided to render a special edition of the Squid Game Mask's.
I wanted to re-use the Logo of Foundation in my Artwork and it turned out really nice.

This Artwork is a special gold edition of my original artwork : Squid Game Mask's - Fan Art that was published in Zbrush Summit, Keyshot commecial d√©mo and many more.
